org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.support
Class AeSupportActivityLocationPathSuffix

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.support.AeSupportActivityLocationPathSuffix
public class AeSupportActivityLocationPathSuffix
extends java.lang.Object

Lists the location paths suffixes used by the support activity. For example, "_ImplicitCompensateActivity".
